title: Kevin Heffernan
description: Kevin Heffernan (Broken Lizard! Super Troopers! Slammin' Salmon!) comes by and makes it weird, "TV fat" style with Pete. So many laughs, so so many Super Trooper questions, and maybe even an impression or two. Get into it... MEOW!
